quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,61,"(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí ẹ wí pé: “Mūsā, a ò níí ṣe ìfaradà lórí oúnjẹ ẹyọ kan. Nítorí náà, pe Olúwa rẹ fún wa. Kí Ó mú jáde fún wa nínú ohun tí ilẹ̀ ń hù jáde ní ewébẹ̀ rẹ̀ àti kùkúḿbà rẹ̀ àti fūmu rẹ̀ (wíìtì àti àlùbọ́sà áyù) àti ọkàbàbà rẹ̀ àti àlùbọ́sà rẹ̀.” (Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ̀yin yóò fi èyí tó yẹpẹrẹ pààrọ̀ èyí tí ó dára jùlọ ni? Ẹ sọ̀kalẹ̀ sínú ìlú (mìíràn). Dájúdájú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń bèèrè fún ń bẹ (níbẹ̀) fún yín.” A sì mú ìyẹpẹrẹ àti òṣì bá wọn. Wọ́n sì padà wálé pẹ̀lú ìbínú láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu. Ìyẹn nítorí pé, dájúdájú wọ́n ń ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn āyah Allāhu, wọ́n sì ń pa àwọn Ànábì láì lẹ́tọ̀ọ́. Ìyẹn nítorí pé, wọ́n yapa (àṣẹ Allāhu), wọ́n sì ń tayọ ẹnu-ààlà."
  2,62,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo àti àwọn yẹhudi àti àwọn nasọ̄rọ̄ àti àwọn sọ̄bi’u; ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú Allāhu àti Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn, tí ó sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, ẹ̀san wọn ń bẹ fún wọn ní ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wọn. Kò sí ìbẹ̀rù fún wọn. Wọn kò sì níí banújẹ́.1 {1}",1:[Irú āyah yìí wà nínú sūrah al-Mọ̄’idah; 5:69 àti sūrah al-Hajj;  22:17.]
  2,63,"Ẹ rántí nígbà tí A gba àdéhùn yín, A sì gbé àpáta wá sókè orí yín, (A sì sọ pé): “Ẹ gbá ohun tí A fún yín mú dáradára, kí ẹ sì rántí ohun tó wà nínú rẹ̀, nítorí kí ẹ lè bẹ̀rù (Allāhu)."
  3,1,"’Alif lām mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)1 {1}",1:[Nítorí kí a lè mọ ìdí pàtàkì tí Allāhu ṣe fi sūrah yìí sọrí mọ̀lẹ́bí ‘Imrọ̄n, òbí Mọryam, ìyá Ànábì ‘Isā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -, ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Mọryam.]
  3,2,"Allāhu, kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun, Alààyè, Alámòjúútó-ẹ̀dá."
  3,3,"Ó sọ Tírà (al-Ƙur’ān) kalẹ̀ fún ọ pẹ̀lú òdodo, ó ń fi ohun tó jẹ́ òdodo rinlẹ̀ nípa èyí tó wà ṣíwájú rẹ̀. Ó sì sọ at-Taorāh àti al-’Injīl kalẹ̀."